      "id": "PopularPost316356",
      "post_content": "FoxdieUK - yes, both [Giant Growth](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Giant Growth) and [Vines of Vastwood](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Vines of Vastwood) could save your creature. [Kira, Great Glass-Spinner](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Kira, Great Glass-Spinner) would also work, as well as a few more things, I'm sure. Protection can't be targeted, sort of like color-hexproof and prevents [Day of Judgement](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Day of Judgement), unless the battlefield affecting spell is stated like this, unpreventable.   \n  \nDarthParallax: To kill Emrakul, somebody must have [Ghostly Flame](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ghostly Flame), for example, in play. If course, one card alone to kill the spaghetti monster is [Baleful Strix](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Baleful Strix).",
